<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-deposit">How to Deposit</h3>
<p>To start betting, you need to put money in your account using Mobile Money. Please simply go to “My Account”. Two options are offered.</p>
<h4 id="online-deposit-">Online deposit:</h4>
<ol>
<li>Enter the amount you want to deposit</li>
<li>Click &quot;Top up now&quot;, then enter your service pin into your phone to authorize the transaction.</li>
<li>Click &quot;Completed&quot;</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="paybill">Paybill</h4>
<ol>
<li>Go to Mpesa menu</li>
<li>Select Payment services</li>
<li>Click on Paybill</li>
<li>Enter business number as 202202</li>
<li>Enter the account number as SportyBet</li>
<li>Enter the amount you want to transfer to SPORTYBET account</li>
<li>Enter your Mpesa pin and Confirm the request</li>
<li>You will shortly receive an SMS from Mpesa to confirm the transaction</li>
</ol>
